{"tid":1922023,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Re.大家慢性自殺緊呢場運動","createTime":"2020-03-12T10:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T12:34:03.000Z","uid":221203,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4daddc18ac8111a0fe6ab442d75cc8929f525c1","tid":1922023,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:14:27.000Z","msg":"小弟最近發現身邊好多人用返淘寶.買大陸野等等 <br />\n宜家連啲香港台灣直播主打lol都去玩國服.一邊叫住光復香港 一邊玩住大陸伺服器 真係開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔出黎幫手運動唔緊要 做文宣share 出國際戰線已經幫咗好大既忙 但最簡單你坐係屋企打機都要去玩大陸野 我真係R撚爆個頭 <br />\n怪唔知得望到愈黎愈多人對呢場運動開始淡（絕對唔係分化.只屌港豬）<br />\n連宜家連登熱門post都係啲on99既post <br />\n前個排 我見到牛丸同個雞丁啲野 大家個個緊張程度仲大過大家講3月8號啲野 我個下真係覺得仲有大撚把人味訓醒 <br />\n但我相信有大部分人會等垃圾肺炎完左 重起號角出發<br />\n大家當幫一幫忙屌一屌醒你身邊既港豬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ecead1c767fe9b7533d3904b542102f75b68a1","tid":1922023,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:14:39.000Z","msg":"推推推推"},{"pid":"70da0e20795c45614f2bbfe1c68368e3cb430b06","tid":1922023,"uid":221203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"推推推推推"},{"pid":"4e58e7a59035f9e380121eb1fb656929a6404795","tid":1922023,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"已經冇淘寶成9個月"},{"pid":"842d1af8dc7b9e9c6105e0f3cf265af63e3dd011","tid":1922023,"uid":258217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:15:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">金拱門都多人去返啦屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"21fa2326099b160a99aeecad0b3547a4026a2ddf","tid":1922023,"uid":133341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T10:16:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n革命唔係請客食飯"},{"pid":"0c5bfc6fb0f67efece972de3c088f00ed8d156f8","tid":1922023,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"842d1af8dc7